--- !u!114 &216191792
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 216191791}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 3127790790c71441cbdc8d59dd2ead68, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  isIntroDialogue: 0
  nodes:
  - speaker: 0
    speakerName: Hazel
    dialogueText: Good morning, Mr. Will
    hasChoices: 0
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 1
    afterAllChoicesNextNode: 0
  - speaker: 1
    speakerName: Will
    dialogueText: 'I know you, the renowned high school detective, Hazel. '
    hasChoices: 0
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 2
    afterAllChoicesNextNode: 0
  - speaker: 1
    speakerName: Will
    dialogueText: ' It''s my great honor to meet you. Although this is not a good
      time.'
    hasChoices: 0
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 3
    afterAllChoicesNextNode: 0
  - speaker: 0
    speakerName: Hazel
    dialogueText: I'd like to ask you, what were you doing at 11:38 when you went
      to see Bob?
    hasChoices: 0
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 4
    afterAllChoicesNextNode: 0
  - speaker: 1
    speakerName: Will
    dialogueText: 'I''ll check with him to confirm the truth to be revealed today. '
    hasChoices: 0
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 5
    afterAllChoicesNextNode: 0
  - speaker: 1
    speakerName: Will
    dialogueText: This is the standard procedure.
    hasChoices: 0
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 6
    afterAllChoicesNextNode: 0
  - speaker: 0
    speakerName: Hazel
    dialogueText: What kind of person do you think Bob is?
    hasChoices: 0
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 7
    afterAllChoicesNextNode: 0
  - speaker: 1
    speakerName: Will
    dialogueText: He is a very good partner, very kind and easy to get along with.
    hasChoices: 0
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 98
    afterAllChoicesNextNode: 0
  - speaker: 1
    speakerName: Will
    dialogueText: However, due to the pressure of work, he sometimes gets a bit grumpy.
    hasChoices: 0
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 10
    afterAllChoicesNextNode: 0
  - speaker: 0
    speakerName: Hazel
    dialogueText: What do you think of Ms. Monica's view that Bob is trying to smear
      her?
    hasChoices: 0
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 11
    afterAllChoicesNextNode: 0
  - speaker: 1
    speakerName: Will
    dialogueText: But it's still acceptable to others.
    hasChoices: 0
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 9
    afterAllChoicesNextNode: 0
  - speaker: 1
    speakerName: Will
    dialogueText: There are always some people who cannot accept the truth.
    hasChoices: 0
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 12
    afterAllChoicesNextNode: 0
  - speaker: 0
    speakerName: Hazel
    dialogueText: How about the Merlin?
    hasChoices: 0
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 13
    afterAllChoicesNextNode: 0
  - speaker: 1
    speakerName: Will
    dialogueText: 'She is a very obedient child who works hard, '
    hasChoices: 0
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 14
    afterAllChoicesNextNode: 0
  - speaker: 1
    speakerName: Will
    dialogueText: but she is not very careful.
    hasChoices: 0
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: 15
    afterAllChoicesNextNode: 0
  - speaker: 0
    speakerName: Hazel
    dialogueText: I understand. Thank you.
    hasChoices: 0
    choices: []
    nextNodeIndex: -1
    afterAllChoicesNextNode: 0
